data.description: Lakeside leisure in the suburbs in this captivating 3-4 bedroom home near Lake Houston. Nestled on a corner cul-de-sac lot, this 2464 sq ft haven redefines modern living.  Unveil endless possibilities with a flex room, ideal for a gym, office or a creative space. The dining room doubles as an elegant office, catering to your work-from-home needs.  Patio offers an expansive screened-in patio, extending your living space.  Positioned on an ample lot, this home offers limitless outdoor potential. Revel in privacy and serenity as you enjoy the cul-de-sac setting. With 3-4 large bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, this home offers comfort and style. The 4th bedroom currently being as a gym can be used as an office/flex or creative space.  Embrace the tranquility of the area, explore lakeside activities, community pool and the balance between convenience and natural beauty.   Your lakeside retreat near Lake Houston awaits.  schedule your tour now!
